{
  "stem": "3100.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Right away, they tried to organize a Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I remember the day when they came in, they took out the eldest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And mostly they took out the [NON-ENGLISH] rabbi and his son, also a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they took out the eldest from the [POLISH], or as we could say, from the Jewish council, the members.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they put them up in the market.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they said, they will shot them to death if they ever wouldn't-- if we wouldn't bring out all the ammunition and arms into there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you know, Jewish people didn't have any revolvers or arms to bring out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So they demanded a certain amount of real coffee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And of course, it was given to them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And a whole day, they was threatening them to shoot, and they let them go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because I think the-- the amount of coffee they received, they were big coffee drinkers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So that saved them, and everybody went back to their homes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then it started a daily struggle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, there was a shortage of food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A while later, they gave out food cards, or stamps, or coupons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And with this we could buy only under their supervision, we could buy only a certain amount of food.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And of course, kosher meat was not available.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was a danger to bring it in, because we were watched, and a struggle.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And once, they caught a kosher butcher selling meat quietly and secretly, they took him out in the front of everybody and they shot him dead.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the struggles began.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
